  ('dietitian-moex-01893', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種微生物污染食品後，以自來水沖洗較能有效防止食物中毒的發生？', '["腸炎弧菌", "李斯特菌", "肉毒桿菌", "產氣莢膜桿菌"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01894', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '河流、湖泊及池塘呈現墨綠色，主要是因為太多水藻在水中繁殖，致使其他生物無法生存，為避 免破壞生態，建議應採用不含下列何種物質的洗潔劑？', '["磷", "氯", "鐵", "鉀"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01895', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關界面活性劑的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["非離子型界面活性劑對水溶性污物的清洗去除，具有很好的效果", "陰離子型界面活性劑具有很強的洗淨力，其活性會因水的硬度影響而增加", "陽離子型界面活性劑，洗淨力差，殺菌力強，常被使用來作為殺菌劑", "兩性型界面活性劑，在溶液中具有正負兩種離子，一般只用來做為清潔劑"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01896', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者是用於檢查餐具上有無蛋白質殘留物存在的檢驗試劑？', '["碘試液", "紅色四號色素酒精試液", "寧海準（ninhydrin）試液", "硫酸鈦溶液"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01897', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '含有β-胡蘿蔔素的黃金米屬於第幾代基因改造作物？', '["第一代", "第二代", "第三代", "第四代"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01898', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '食品業者之從業人員、作業場所、設施衛生管理及其品保制度，應符合下列何種規定？', '["食品良好作業規範準則", "食品良好衛生規範準則", "食品安全管制系統準則", "食品衛生標準準則"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01899', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '以基因改造生物做為食品時，應進行下列幾項之安全性評估？①新的毒性物質產生  ②過敏原含', '["營養組成改變", "殖入基因發生轉移  ⑤抗生素標示基因是否表現", "2", "3"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc7609492beb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3346080f7eeb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01900', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-107-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'essay', '106 年 11 月衛生福利部國民健康署結合臺中市、臺南市及花蓮縣成立社區營養推
廣中心，以社區銀髮族及上班族為對象，聘請營養師走入社區推動健康均衡飲食，
教導民眾如何「吃得下、吃得夠、吃得對、吃得巧」。現在你所在的縣市也即將推
廣本計畫，請你規劃一系列以社區銀髮族為推廣對象的相關課程，說明你會如何進
行？（15分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0bfeb6891da2", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "103", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01901', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-107-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'essay', '身為公共衛生營養師，須配合當地衛生局進行營養活動之推廣。此次以青少年為主
要活動對象，宣導減少含糖飲料攝取為目標，並利用社交媒體（如：facebook, twitter,
Youtube, Flickr 等等….）為主要設計工具。請說明使用此方法之優缺點及注意事
項，並請舉出本計畫所涵蓋之內容。（15分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0bfeb6891da2", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "103", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01902', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-107-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'essay', '有民眾詢問營養師：“食物中膽固醇不等於血中膽固醇，對於高膽固醇食物的攝取
